---
title: Beef Tenderloin with Brown Butter Veggies plus Parmesan Mashed Potatoes
description: Beef tenderloin is extra special. True to its name, this cut is luxuriously tender—perfect for impressing your dinner companion (and yourself). Here, it’s seared and then drizzled with an ultra-savory shallot pan sauce. The sides might just steal the show though. We’re serving up creamy Parmesan mashed potatoes and roasted carrots and parsnips tossed with nutty brown butter... Because everything is better with butter!
